    "params" : { "workflow-id" : 0, "is-release" : true, "resolution-hash" : "0xhash" }
  }, {
    "seq" : 3, "time" : 1130, "agent" : "buyer", "action" : "escalate_dispute",
    "params" : { "workflow-id" : 0 }
  } ],
  "scenario-notes" : "escalation-resolvers maps level 0->0xl0 and level 2->0xl2 but omits level 1. When buyer escalates after L0 resolution, escalation-fn seeks resolver for level 1 from level-map → nil → returns {:ok false :error :escalation-not-allowed}. The missing level causes clean rejection.",
